Descriptive.ExpeditionDescription: Local override to Sector Gamma lockdown discovered. Disposable prisoners dispatched
Descriptive.RoleplayedWardenIntel:
>… We've got to move quickly.
>… Wait... Why is it closing?
>… <color=red><size=200%>Oh Shit</size></color>

Descriptive.ExpeditionDescription: Datasphere containing data about the location of A-3261 located. Prisoners dispatched to retrieve it.
Descriptive.RoleplayedWardenIntel:
>… This stupid thing needs to go faster.
>… I don't know how much longer we can last?
>… Just buckle donwn and <color=red><size=200%>keep shooting</size></color>

Descriptive.ExpeditionDescription: Prisoners dispatched to distribute Power Cells to local area. Success unlikely
Descriptive.RoleplayedWardenIntel:
>… We've got to put in these cells.
>… Let's <color=red><size=200%>not stick around</size></color>

Descriptive.ExpeditionDescription: Secondary team required for assistance in reactor startup process. Prisoners dispatched for code aquisition
Descriptive.RoleplayedWardenIntel:
>… Send the code now.
>… I'm trying. I'm trying.
 [Distant Screams] 
>… I've got <color=red><size=200%>No Connection</size></color>
